- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper deals with data trees and their properties.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) could be a possible category as the paper discusses the expressiveness of different models of computation.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) could also be relevant as the paper deals with decision problems and their complexity.
